{"type":"message","id":"96e3f803","parentId":"7b8170c8","timestamp":"2026-04-02T12:55:19.081Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:6","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"war-room  War Room  Multi-agent war room for brainstorming, system design, architecture review, product specs, business strategy, or any complex problem. Use when a user wants to run a structured multi-agent session with specialist roles, when they mention \"war room\", when they need to brainstorm a project from scratch, design a system with multiple perspectives, stress-test decisions with a devil's advocate, or produce a comprehensive blueprint/spec. Works for software, hardware, content, business — any domain.\nsw-war-room  War Room Debug  Facilitates coordinated crisis response using multiple agents to assess, investigate, fix, and document critical production issues efficiently.\niris-war-room  War Room — Adversarial Decision Engine  Run adversarial multi-agent war-room evaluations for any strategic decision. Spawns 5 parallel subagents (Analyst, Guardian, Treasurer, Builder, Strategist)...\nbriefing-room  Briefing Room  Daily news briefing generator — produces a conversational radio-host-style audio briefing + DOCX document covering weather, X/Twitter trends, web trends, world news, politics, tech, local news, sports, markets, and crypto. macOS only (uses Apple TTS and afplay). Use when user asks for a news briefing, morning briefing, daily update, or similar.\nwar-intel-monitor  War Intelligence Monitor  Real-time war intelligence monitoring and emergency alert system for conflict zones. Use when user needs to track military conflicts, receive emergency alert...\nagent-arena  Agent Arena Skill  Participate in Agent Arena chat rooms with your real personality (SOUL.md + MEMORY.md). Auto-polls for turns and responds as your true self.\nafrexai-warehouse-ops  Warehouse Operations Optimizer  Analyze warehouse setup to optimize space, labor, picking efficiency, inventory accuracy, cost per order, automation ROI, and safety compliance with a priori...\nclawroom  Clawroom  Create or join a ClawRoom (agent meeting room) with safe defaults and owner confirmation. Use when the user mentions ClawRoom, agent meetings, or multi-agent...\nchat-rooom  Chat Rooom  Create local chat rooms for AI agents with channels, mentions, task claims, and durable summaries in the workspace.\nmycelium-io  Mycelium  Use the mycelium CLI to join coordination rooms, negotiate with other agents via CognitiveEngine, and share persistent memory across sessions."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3393,"aggregated":"war-room  War Room  Multi-agent war room for brainstorming, system design, architecture review, product specs, business strategy, or any complex problem. Use when a user wants to run a structured multi-agent session with specialist roles, when they mention \"war room\", when they need to brainstorm a project from scratch, design a system with multiple perspectives, stress-test decisions with a devil's advocate, or produce a comprehensive blueprint/spec. Works for software, hardware, content, business — any domain.\nsw-war-room  War Room Debug  Facilitates coordinated crisis response using multiple agents to assess, investigate, fix, and document critical production issues efficiently.\niris-war-room  War Room — Adversarial Decision Engine  Run adversarial multi-agent war-room evaluations for any strategic decision. Spawns 5 parallel subagents (Analyst, Guardian, Treasurer, Builder, Strategist)...\nbriefing-room  Briefing Room  Daily news briefing generator — produces a conversational radio-host-style audio briefing + DOCX document covering weather, X/Twitter trends, web trends, world news, politics, tech, local news, sports, markets, and crypto. macOS only (uses Apple TTS and afplay). Use when user asks for a news briefing, morning briefing, daily update, or similar.\nwar-intel-monitor  War Intelligence Monitor  Real-time 